OL,3,CFindings of public inquiry into
OL,4,CSouthport attack to be published
OL,6,FThe findings of a public inquiry into
OL,7,Fthe Southport attack, which claimed
OL,8,Fthe lives of three young girls, are to
OL,9,Fbe published.
OL,11,FThe Southport Inquiry heard evidence
OL,12,Fabout the attack on 29 July 2024 and
OL,13,Fthe involvement of state agencies with
OL,14,Fthe 19-year-old killer in the lead up
OL,15,Fto it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
