CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776082266
OL,3,CFindings of public inquiry into
OL,4,CSouthport attack to be published
OL,6,FAlice da Silva Aguiar, nine, Bebe
OL,7,FKing, six, and Elsie Dot Stancombe,
OL,8,Fseven, were murdered when the knifeman
OL,9,Fentered the Taylor Swift-themed dance
OL,10,Fworkshop in The Hart Space, armed with
OL,11,Fa knife.
OL,13,FThe killer, then 17, also attempted to
OL,14,Fmurder eight other children, who
OL,15,Fcannot be named for legal reasons,
OL,16,Fclass instructor Leanne Lucas, and
OL,17,Fbusinessman John Hayes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
