FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776082266
OL,3,CFindings of public inquiry into
OL,4,CSouthport attack to be published
OL,6,FThe inquiry, held over nine weeks at
OL,7,FLiverpool Town Hall in 2025, heard
OL,8,Ffrom more than 100 witnesses, 67 who
OL,9,Fgave live evidence, about topics
OL,10,Fincluding the killer's involvement
OL,11,Fwith health services, social care and
OL,12,Feducation.
OL,14,FIt also examined three referrals to
OL,15,Fanti-terror programme Prevent which
OL,16,Fwere made, and closed, before he
OL,17,Fcarried out the attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
