PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776082266
OL,3,CFindings of public inquiry into
OL,4,CSouthport attack to be published
OL,6,FSolicitor Nicola Brook from Broudie
OL,7,FJackson Canter, who represent Ms
OL,8,FLucas, Mr Hayes and another adult
OL,9,Fsurvivor, Heidi Liddle, said: "Sitting
OL,10,Fthrough the extensive list of failings
OL,11,Fexposed during the first phase of the
OL,12,Finquiry provoked an understandably
OL,13,Fcomplex mix of emotions for our
OL,14,Fclients, who battle the daily
OL,15,Fconsequences of survivors' guilt.
OL,26,@qD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776082266
OL,3,CFindings of public inquiry into
OL,4,CSouthport attack to be published
OL,6,F"We hope the report will expose every
OL,7,Fentity that failed to act in time to
OL,8,Fprevent this catastrophic attack, and
OL,9,Fany agencies that are found to be at
OL,10,Ffault are committed to not just
OL,11,Flearning lessons but demonstrating,
OL,12,Fpublicly, that they are committed to
OL,13,Ftaking every step to prevent such an
OL,14,Fatrocity from happening again.
OL,16,F"We cannot look back on this inquiry
OL,17,Fin years to come and summarise it as
OL,18,Fanother navel-gazing exercise for the
OL,19,FGovernment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776082266
OL,3,CFindings of public inquiry into
OL,4,CSouthport attack to be published
OL,6,F"There is no regulatory mechanism to
OL,7,Fensure that recommendations are
OL,8,Fproperly considered and acted upon at
OL,9,Fthe end of an inquiry, which is why we
OL,10,Fare strongly urging the chair to
OL,11,Fimplement a process to monitor the
OL,12,Fprogress of all recommendations and
OL,13,Fprovide evidence to support them, as
OL,14,Fhappened at the Manchester Arena
OL,15,FInquiry.
OL,17,F"Since that harrowing day, our
OL,18,Fclients' thoughts have remained with
OL,19,Fthe bereaved and will remain so today."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU{D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
