PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1776082266
OL,3,CFindings of public inquiry into
OL,4,CSouthport attack to be published
OL,6,FChairman Sir Adrian Fulford, who will
OL,7,Fpublish his report at midday on
OL,8,FMonday, 13 April, said the obligation
OL,9,Fwas to provide answers to victims and
OL,10,Ftheir families.
OL,12,FConcluding the hearings in November,
OL,13,Fhe said: "Our principal responsibility
OL,14,Flies to them, to provide the best
OL,15,Fpossible explanation as to why and how
OL,16,Fthis terrible event occurred, and to
OL,17,Fbe brave about suggesting the changes
OL,18,Fthat ought to be made to prevent, if
OL,19,Fwe can, a repetition."
OL,26,@uD@JOU{D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
