OL,3,CFindings of public inquiry into
OL,4,CSouthport attack to be published
OL,6,FA second phase of the inquiry will be
OL,7,Finformed by the findings of phase one
OL,8,Fand is expected to focus on the risk
OL,9,Fposed by young people with a fixation,
OL,10,For obsession with, acts of extreme
OL,11,Fviolence.
OL,13,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,14,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,15,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,16,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
